Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（接受）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里 只是看在我父母\NI only came here out of respect for my parents who...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认识你家族的分上\NKnew your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令尊对我的家族而言 不只是一位朋友\NYour father was more than just a friend to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事了\NThat was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前的事了\NA long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤玛士韦恩相信家父\NThomas Wayne believed in my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他相信人能让混乱的世界恢复秩序\NHe believed a man could bring order to a world of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯 你呢？\NAnd you, Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信高谭市\NI believe in Gotham city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-尝过蛤蜊义大利面了吗？   -好吃\N- You try the vongole?   - Mm. Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（法官办公室）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（当选人 哈维丹特）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯少爷 万圣节快乐\NMaster Bruce. Happy Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有咖啡吗？   - 已经送到书房了 少爷\N- Is there coffee?   - In the study, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有位凯尔小姐打过电话\NA miss Kyle telephoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说想确认你给的号码是真的\NShe said she was checking the number you gave her to make sure it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大门都开了 好几年没看到讨糖的人了\NThe gates are open. We haven't seen a trick-or-treater in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不会看到了\NWe won't see one tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不值得冒险 对吧？\NHardly worth the security risk, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言 少爷\NRespectfully, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们的安全 依赖的是六百美元的铁合金…\Nif our security is dependent on $600 worth of iron alloy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市已经跌入深渊 阿福\NThis city is fallen, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们得努力让它再站起来 布鲁斯\NThen we must endeavor to lift it up again, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此同时 我们拥有顽强的意志力\NIn the meantime, we live in obstinate hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有没上锁的豪宅\NAnd an unlocked mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 这是个荒谬的节日\NAnyway... It's an absurd holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 换上奇装异服 搞得人心惶惶\NOh, yes. Putting on costumes and striking fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确荒谬\NQuite absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的认为…\NDo you really think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌他这样\NI hate when he does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯 小芭 别跑来跑去\NJames, babs! No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别跑了 你们会受伤的\NCome on, guys, slow down. You're gonna hurt yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很兴奋 吉姆 今晚很热闹\NThey're excited, Jim. Big night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但我们要开警车\NYeah. All right. But we're taking the squad car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面太多疯子了\NToo many crazies out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\NHang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备好了\NNow, you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 谁想开车？\NAll right, who wants to drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆\NJim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的\NJust joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 等等\NHey, hey, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是打错电话 或恶作剧…\NIt could be a wrong number, or a crank call or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高登\NGordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我马上过去\NAll right. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸现在是队长了\NYour father's captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个警局都依赖他\NThe whole department's counting on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很依赖他\NWell, I was counting on him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽快回来\NI'll try and be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊 吉尔达\NGilda, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维\NHarvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你回来了   - 晚到总比不到好\N- You're home.   - Better late than never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么躲在外面吹冷风？\NWhy are you hiding out here in the cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我只是…\NI know. I'm sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没等我就开始了\NMm, you started without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小孩吗？\NDid you have any kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨糖的小孩\NTrick-or-treaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有…我… 我只是…\NOh, no. I don't... no. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚没那个兴致\NI don't think I'm really up for all that tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每五分钟开一次门\NAnswering the door every five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持微笑\NSmiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我看到门廊上的碗了\NYeah, I saw the bowl on the porch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 这座镇上没什么人\NIt's okay. It's a ghost town out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧\NSo to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那碗糖我们会吃一个月\NWe're gonna be eating that candy for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者不会\NOr not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我对糖果又爱又恨\NYou know I have a love-hate relationship with candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对所有东西都又爱又恨\NYou have a love-hate relationship with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们躺在床上\NLet's just crawl into bed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看部黑白电影…\Nand watch an old black and white movie on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 很抱歉\NBaby, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去忙了\NYou have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影你选 我马上回来\NPick a movie. I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他老是让你在这里等吗？\NDoes he always keep you waiting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会来的\NHe'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你戒了\NI thought you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是戒了\NI have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我不会告诉芭芭拉的\NHmm. Don't worry, I won't tell Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位\NGentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NAh. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是地方检察官哈维丹…\NThis is district attorney Harvey d...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠侠\NBats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹特\NDent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\NWhat's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼维提今晚遭到谋杀\NJohnny viti was murdered tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马人的侄子\NThe Roman's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有名字\NHe has a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫卡麦法尔康尼 不叫罗马人…\NIt's carmine Falcone, not "the Roman."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别激动 哈维\NHarvey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人呢 吉姆？ 我已经调查维提好几个月了\NWhere were your men, Jim? I've been working on viti for months!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你队上就没半个人想到\NNobody on your team thought he'd be vulnerable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在转污点证人前一晚 会有危险吗？\Nthe night before he's gonna turn state's evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:12:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点22口径 枪把包着胶带 序号磨掉了\N22 caliber, taped handle, serial number filed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用奶瓶嘴当消音器 很怪 但很管用\NBaby bottle nipple for a silencer. Odd, but effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且无法追踪\NAnd untraceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难判断是否是职业杀手\NHard to tell if we're dealing with a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是职业杀手 是法尔康尼干的\NOf course it was a professional! This was Falcone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他发现维提要背叛家族\NHe found out viti was gonna betray the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是做掉他\Nso he took him off the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只差一步就能拿下他们了\NWe were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就差一步 吉姆\NWe were so close, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼本来决定要告发他们\NHe was ready to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只卡麦 整个家族都会遭殃\NAnd not just about carmine, the whole family was going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来有大好机会 能改变一切\NWe had a real opportunity to change things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机会还在 目前只是遇到挫折\NWe still do. It's just a setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会找到方法击溃法尔康尼家族\NWe'll find another way to take down Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起\NTogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南瓜灯在哪里？\NWhere's the Jack-o'-lantern?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这很重要吗？\NYou think it's important?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说不准\NI don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维说得对\NLook, Harvey's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高谭市好不容易有机会\NThis city's finally got a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就靠我们三个了\NAnd it's the three men standing here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须击垮法尔康尼犯罪家族\NThe Falcone crime family has to be taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们两个合作\NSo, I'm putting you two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹特检察官负责白天行动 而你\NDistrict attorney dent will work in the light, and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责夜晚\NWill work the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随机应变 但不要违法\NBend the rules, but never break them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力保护你们两个\NAnd I'll do everything I can to protect you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他必须得到你的承诺 蝙蝠侠\NHe needs to hear you say it, bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人多力量大\NTwo heads are better than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线索来得很快\NLeads come my way pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持警戒\NKeep your ears open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我想我们准备好\NThen I guess we're up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行动了\NRunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他常那样 我已经…\NHe does that a lot. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩我自言自语\NAnd I'm talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父\NGodfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您侄子的事 请节哀\NI'm so sorry to hear about your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 朋友\NGrazie, amico.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡麦\NCarmine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无意冒犯 但为什么我们什么都不做？\Nno disrespect but why are we sitting on our hands here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对强尼开了两枪\NHe put two in Johnny's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁干的？\NWho did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是萨尔瓦多马洛尼还有谁\NSalvatore maroni! Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从他接掌他家 就一直想除掉我们\NEver since he took over that family, he's been gunning for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚他找到了目标\Nand tonight he found the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在警告我们\NIt's a warning, for chrissakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\NPerhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但先讲清楚\NBut let us be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的人不是上膛的人\NThe man who pulled the trigger did not load the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在司法针对我以前 马洛尼不曾轻举妄动\NMaroni's ambition was in check until the law put a target on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是打猎季节\NNow, it's open season.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要说是谁害死我侄子\NIf anyone is responsible for my nephew's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是地方检察署那个混蛋\Nit's that new son of a bitch in the da's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹特\NDent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错   -也许该除掉他\N- Mm-hmm. Yeah.   - Maybe he should sleep with the fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NHell yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡麦 只要你下令 我就亲自解决丹特\NYou just say the word, carmine, and I'll do dent myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷静 安东尼\NSettle, antoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等时机成熟 我们会报仇 在那之前…\NAt the right time, we'll hit back. Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 卡麦\NThe right time is now, carmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再拖下去 只会让你看起来更懦弱\NNow! Any delay is only gonna make you look even weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你关心 安东尼\NThank you for your concern, antoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无意冒犯 卡麦\NNo disrespect, carmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是“教父”\NIt's "godfather."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米洛斯 别这样\NMilos. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米洛斯 不\NMilos! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNol
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的事要谈吗？\NWe have other business to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝托？\NAlberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝托\NAlberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在谈正事\NBusiness time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿你的字谜游戏出去玩吧\NTake your crosswords for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…逻辑谜题\NThey're... logic puzzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,32岁了还像13岁一样\NThirty-two going on 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦恩不会支援大型建案\NWayne is not gonna support any large-scale structuring effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在得暂时把资产移到更安全的地方\NSo, for now, the assets will have to be moved to a more secure facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的装备拖垮了你\NYour equipment's weighing you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要跑？\NWhy are you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好玩啊 你需要来点乐子\NFun. You could use a little fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手给我\NGive me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总算把你引来我要的地方\NGot you exactly where I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼\NFalcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你看了里头的东西再说吧\NWalt till you see what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过这么多钱吗？\NHave you ever seen this kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真钞\NIt's authentic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此乾净\NSo crisp and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是脏钱\NActually, it's incredibly dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼最近洗钱不太顺利\NFalcone's been having trouble laundering his cash for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是不知道钱藏在哪\NWe just didn't know where he was stockpiling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意帮忙\NI'm happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大可据为己有\NYou could have kept it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些钱能让你过上好日子\NYou could have lived pretty well with all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要交出来？\NWhy hand it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给你？\NTo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道？\NWho knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我一句 朋友 在这里 好奇心会害死你\NTake it from me, pal, around here, curiosity can get you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了他\NLet him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？为什么？\NWhat? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同夥\NBecause he's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这位检察官 把你朋友全送进阿卡汉的\NAlso, because he's the da who put all your friends into arkham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有一间空房\NWe got room for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人跟来吗？\NAnyone follow us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都快跟不上了\NI could barely follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼进口公司搞了一番大事业啊\NFalcone imports has been doing quite a business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 如果我们像其他人…\NYou know, if we were any other men...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是\NWe're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是\NYeah. No. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办？\NSo, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该叫高登来一趟\NWe should call Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请他的人把钱带回去当证据\NHave his men pick this up as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市长和市议会都听法尔康尼使唤\NFalcone owns the mayor and the entire city assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天这些钱就会回到他的金库\NIt'd be back in his coffers by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以唯一有效的办法就是让钱消失\NSo, the only way to make an impact is to make it disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但看看这些钱 光是移动就要好几天\NYeah, but look at all this. Moving it could take days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要移动了？\NWell, who said anything about moving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要惹法尔康尼？\NWhy are you trying to hurt Falcone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？\NWhy are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无关私人恩怨 亲爱的 只是伸张正义\NIt's not personal, sweetheart. It's justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正义也可以是私人恩怨 亲爱的\NJustice can be personal, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步\NGive me a head start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想在这里被抓\NI don't want to get caught anywhere near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高登说我负责白天行动\NGordon says I'm supposed to work in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就照亮这里吧\NWell, then, light it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你一次\NI owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我的次数…难以估计\NYou owe me, like... A billion-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能既是律师又是罪犯 对吧？\NI can't really be a lawyer and a criminal, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想赢\NI want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的想靠这个赢吗？\NBut do I want to win like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法决定\NI'm of two minds here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丢钱币决定\NSo, it's a coin flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好这样了\NYeah, I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人头 就全烧光\NHeads, we burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把陈叫来\NCall chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消防员来到工业区\NFirefighters on the scene here in the industrial district
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试图控制火势\Nworking to contain the Blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以免波及邻近住家及店家\Nbefore it can spread to nearby homes and businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贾吉 目前\NNow, at this time, Jackie,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,官方认为 恶名昭彰的法尔康尼犯罪家族\Nofficials believe the Falcone imports warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所拥有的这间公司仓库\Nowned, of course, by the notorious Falcone crime family,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里头空无一人\Nto be vacant...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“人多力量大”\N"Two heads are better than one."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.65,0:24:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔达？\NGilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔达？\NGilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.04,0:25:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你吓到我了\NHey! You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.50,0:25:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来找不到你\NI came home and I didn't know where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.51,0:25:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有听到我叫你吗？\NDid you hear me calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.01,0:25:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你留下来\NPlease stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.72,0:25:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不会去\NI'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.26,0:25:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的 别离开我\NI mean it. Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.43,0:25:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 我知道我最近很忙\NBaby, I know I haven't been around. And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\NBut this job...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这个工作只是暂时的\NIt isn't forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.65,0:25:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼的案子今晚大有斩获\NHey, we caught a huge break tonight on this Falcone thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.45,0:25:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我击垮他 我会击垮他的\NOnce I take him out, and I will take him out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.70,0:25:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切就会改变了\Nthings are gonna be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.87,0:25:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能生孩子\NWe can start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.42,0:25:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不能\NYou know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.54,0:25:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然可以 我们可以的\NOf course you can. We can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你准备好 我们再来计划\NWe'll talk about options when you're ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.67,0:25:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要你相信我们办得到\Nbut I need you to trust that we're still on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.59,0:26:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我很爱你\NAnd that I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.47,0:26:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的电影还算数吗？\NNow, are we still having movie night, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.14,0:26:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 别回答 走吧\NNo, don't even answer that. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.94,0:26:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走66街就能在西向大桥拦截他们\NIf we take 66th, we can cut them off at the westward bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:27:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 先保持安全距离\NNo. Maintain a safe distance for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 少爷 火鸡正在烤\NGood evening, sir. The Turkey is roasting,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.89,0:27:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派已经凉了 凯尔小姐正在路上\Nthe pies are cooling, and miss Kyle is en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.48,0:27:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿福 记得订新的挡风玻璃\NAlfred, make a note to order a new windshield.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.94,0:27:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要防弹的\NBulletproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.11,0:27:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 少爷 但容我…\NOf course, sir, but if I may...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.08,0:28:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（中国城）\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.26,0:28:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不会伤人\NI thought you didn't hurt people!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.31,0:28:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了\NYou thought wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.06,0:28:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看到你和三合会同夥\NYou and your San ho hui buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.94,0:29:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万圣节出现在哈维丹特家门外\Nwere seen outside Harvey dent's house on Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.11,0:29:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是去讨糖\NWe were trick-or-treating.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.86,0:29:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好玩吗？\NHaving fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.66,0:29:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始呢\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.24,0:29:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会好玩了\NBut any second now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.53,0:29:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.24,0:31:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会盯好这些小朋友\NGo. I'll keep an eye on your little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:32:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时应该说声“谢谢”\NA "thank you" would be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.96,0:32:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是感恩节\NIt is Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以速战速决 米奇\NWe can make this easy, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.51,0:32:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要告诉我 是谁雇你去杀丹特\NJust tell me who hired you to kill dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.68,0:32:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 死蝙蝠\NGo to hell, bat-freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.65,0:32:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我俩唯一的不同是\NRight now, the only difference between you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.52,0:32:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这下面有什么\Nis that I know what's down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格兰迪\NGrundy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.92,0:32:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的\NHe's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.63,0:32:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了他\NLet him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.80,0:32:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的地盘\NThis is your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他交给我 我保证他不会再出现在这里\NGive him to me and I'll make sure he never sets foot down here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.31,0:33:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以一个人待在这里\NYou can be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.92,0:33:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期一出生\NBorn on a Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.52,0:33:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来一束花\NOne more for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.60,0:33:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\NMy goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.61,0:33:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都对哈维很好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.77,0:33:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是给你先生的 是给你的\NOh, this one's not for your husband. It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.24,0:33:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自“法尔康尼先生”\NFrom a "Mr. Falcone."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.54,0:34:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 女士\NI'm sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.96,0:34:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不关我的事…\NIt's none of my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.92,0:34:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的晚餐时间不是到了吗？\NIsn't it time for his dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.05,0:34:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想来这里 米奇\NI don't wanna be here, Mick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.39,0:34:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太在忙着准备火鸡大餐\NMy wife's cooking Turkey with all the trimmings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.77,0:34:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢火鸡大餐\NI love Turkey with all the trimmings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.35,0:34:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检察官家爆炸\NSo, just tell us what you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.31,0:34:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么内幕 和盘托出\Nabout the bomb in the district attorney's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.32,0:34:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能去吃大餐了\Nthen we can all go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.44,0:34:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不认识卡麦法尔康尼\NI don't even know carmine Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.70,0:34:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马人雇了你的三合会 去解决哈维丹特\NThe Roman contracted your triad to take out Harvey dent!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.58,0:34:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全是你的作案手法\NYour signature's all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.50,0:34:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 你得帮我安抚我的朋友\NMickey, you gotta help me keep my friend here calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.33,0:34:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要告诉我们 任何线索都好\NJust give us something... Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想陷害我\NSomeone's trying to frame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.88,0:34:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 我是清白的\NI told you. I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.18,0:35:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椅子是给嫌犯坐的\NChairs are for suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.89,0:35:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是清白的\NThis guy's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为只是要吓吓他\NHey. I thought we were just doing a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.85,0:35:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这家伙受伤 我们就功亏一篑了\NThis little act doesn't get us anywhere if the guy gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.61,0:35:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们应该承认 你们没有三合会的把柄\NMaybe you guys should admit you have nothing on San ho hui.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则早就逮捕我了\NIf you had, you would've booked me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.53,0:35:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 够了 蒙托亚\NAll right. That's it. Montoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.03,0:35:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请带这位朋友出去\NPlease, show our friend out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你该谢谢那位炸弹客\NMaybe you should thank whoever planted that bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.50,0:35:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.58,0:35:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白是谁杀了强尼维提吗？\NYou still haven't figured out who killed Johnny viti?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.59,0:35:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他带走\NGet him outta my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.76,0:35:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也许擅长拳脚功夫\NYou may be aces in a fistfight,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但查案你还有很多要学\Nbut you've got a lot to learn about detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.31,0:35:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我找到他的 不是吗？\NI found him, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.77,0:35:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到他们还不够\NIt's not just about finding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得知道怎么利用他们破案\NYou gotta know how they're gonna help your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.81,0:35:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陈米奇背後有法尔康尼罩着\NMickey chen is a small fish protected by Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.82,0:35:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远拿不到自白\NWe were never going to get a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.15,0:36:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该跟他们交朋友 最後劝他们当污点证人\NWe needed to make friends and, in time, flip him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.03,0:36:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续说下去 有人会找你当检察官\NKeep talking like that, they'll make you da.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.87,0:36:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维还没死\NHarvey isn't dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.29,0:36:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也不是凶手\NAnd he isn't a killer, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.96,0:36:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论那个人渣怎么想\NNo matter what that scumbag thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.71,0:36:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他连枪都没有\NHe's never even owned a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼有\NFalcone fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.55,0:36:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马人杀了维提 然後买凶杀害丹特\NThe Roman killed viti and ordered the hit on dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.55,0:36:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥坎剃刀法则\NOccam's razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.47,0:36:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最简单的解释通常是正确的\NThe simplest explanation is usually the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.35,0:36:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我现在走 可能赶得上晚餐\NAll right. If I leave now, I might just make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.39,0:36:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该跟家人团聚\NYou should be with your people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.65,0:36:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.57,0:36:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.83,0:36:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感恩节快乐 丹特太太\NHappy Thanksgiving, Mrs. dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.29,0:36:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人一定是去外面享用餐点\NNow, I'm sure the missus is running out to pick up some real food,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.62,0:36:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我向你保证 这南瓜派你绝对没…\Nbut I guarantee you, you have never had pumpkin pie like...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.05,0:37:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹特先生？\NUh, Mr. dent?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.43,0:37:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想离开这座城市 我讨厌这里\NI just, you know, wanna get out of the city, I hate this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.14,0:37:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\NNice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.19,0:37:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘诀在罗勒\NThe secret is the basil.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.86,0:37:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能用最嫩的叶子\NYou want only the youngest leaves from the youngest plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.20,0:37:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则就像薄荷叶\Notherwise, it's like mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.12,0:37:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喧宾夺主\NOverpowers everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.04,0:37:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有很多事要感恩 阿尔贝托\NWe have a lot to be thankful for, Alberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.67,0:37:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如？\NSuch as?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.83,0:37:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健康、家人\NHealth. Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.67,0:37:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅剩的家人\NWhat's left of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你指的是你表哥强尼\NIf you are referring to your cousin Johnny,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.13,0:37:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事已经处理好了\Nthat is being handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.80,0:37:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陈米奇办好了\NBy Mickey chen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.60,0:37:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁雇用他的？\NAnd who do you think hired him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.06,0:37:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.61,0:38:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么吗？\NIs there something you wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.99,0:38:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 父亲\NNo, poppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.49,0:38:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想说 哈维丹特还活着\NExcept to point out that Harvey dent is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.83,0:38:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我允许他活着的\NBecause I allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.16,0:38:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时活着\NFor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.29,0:38:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…\NThis...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.88,0:38:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我一直在说的\NThis is what I keep talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.34,0:38:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是牛津大学害的\NThis is Oxford.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.88,0:38:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方污染了你的脑袋 阿尔贝托\NThat place polluted your mind, Alberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.26,0:38:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前很安分守己 现在呢？\NYou used to know your place. Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.59,0:38:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初不该送你去的\NI should have never sent you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.64,0:38:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独立思考的危险\NThe dangers of independent thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.65,0:38:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有过任何想法\NWhen have you had one independent thought
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.11,0:38:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真正对这个家有帮助的吗？\Nthat actually benefited this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.69,0:38:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以法尔康尼的名义送花到医院\NMaybe when I sent flowers to dent's hospital room
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.66,0:38:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给丹特的时候\Nin the Falcone name.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？\NYou did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.45,0:38:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送花过去\NI sent flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.12,0:38:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们关心他的复原状况\NI thought it would take suspicion off of us
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.21,0:39:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能摆脱嫌疑\Nif we looked like we care about his recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.67,0:39:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会说这是草率的行为\NNow, I suppose you'll say it was a sloppy move.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.05,0:39:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以原谅草率的行为\NI can forgive sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.35,0:39:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忍受的是\NWhat I will not tolerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.60,0:39:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自作主张 代表这个家发声\Nis you presuming to speak on behalf of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.40,0:39:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我再跟你\NLet me be perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.86,0:39:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚\NAgain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.53,0:39:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你指望\NAny notion you may hold about being next in line
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.70,0:39:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接掌整个家族事业\Nto take over our business interests
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.46,0:39:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用痴心妄想\Nis a pathetic delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.47,0:39:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真懦弱\NYou are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.05,0:39:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的懦弱只会扯我後腿\NYour weakness is my liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.31,0:39:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准你再去找丹特夫妇\NYou are to have zero contact with Mr. or Mrs. Harvey dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.89,0:40:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说完了\NEnd of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维\NHarvey!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.71,0:41:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.25,0:41:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接到电话说你在医院失踪\NI got a call that you went missing from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.09,0:41:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁想得到你会在这里\NHow did I know I'd find you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.68,0:41:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再被关在那里了\NCouldn't stand being cooped up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.51,0:41:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想出来动一动\NThought I'd stretch my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.76,0:41:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.26,0:41:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车吧 我载你回去\NListen, why don't you hop in? I'll take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.93,0:41:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我喜欢待在这里\NOh, no. No. No. No. No. I like it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.02,0:41:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正要回家吃感恩节晚餐\NI'm on my way home for Thanksgiving dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.65,0:41:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吧 芭芭拉老是煮一堆\NYou should come along. Barbara always makes a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不饿\NI'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.62,0:41:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维 我们在这里做什么？\NHarvey, what are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 也许我还没准备好\NI don't know. Maybe I wasn't ready for this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.96,0:41:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我该回去了\NI think I'm gonna go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.30,0:41:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心哈维\NDon't you worry about Harvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.84,0:41:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 律师\NAll right, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.81,0:42:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 你没有这把枪\NAs far as I'm concerned, you don't have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.56,0:42:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼家族是危险分子 他们视你为眼中钉\NThe falcones are dangerous people and, to them, you're the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.82,0:42:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护好家人\NProtect your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我开了个条件给他\NSo, I made him an offer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬家人\NTo the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.10,0:42:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬离开我们的挚爱…\NThose dearly departed...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.31,0:42:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及有幸还在身边的家人\NAnd those whom we are fortunate to have beside us here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.98,0:42:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们感恩能在此团聚\NLet us be thankful for the time we still have together
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.44,0:42:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并拥有许多祝福\Nand for the many blessings bestowed upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.53,0:42:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-乾杯   -乾杯\N- Alla salute!   - Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.67,0:43:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NAh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你看   -快过来\N- Oh, look.   - Oh, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.84,0:43:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶\N- Oh-ho!   - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.05,0:43:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就说我会出来的   -很好\N- I told you I'd walk.   - Very good. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.63,0:43:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.51,0:43:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来\NWelcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.07,0:43:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芭芭拉？\NBarbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.95,0:44:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门格兰迪…\NSolomon grundy...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.91,0:44:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期一出生\NBorn on a Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.72,0:44:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 我教他怎么钉住披风\NBelieve me, I told him where he could stick the cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.85,0:44:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连高登都笑了\NEven Gordon laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.81,0:44:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就放我走了\NThat's when they let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.66,0:45:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（感恩节）
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.59,0:45:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要找我来 我应该在外面调查才对\NYou don't need me for this. I should be out hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.76,0:45:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都处理好了\NWe've got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.10,0:45:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有警察午夜前会布署在全城\NAll of Gotham pd will be deployed throughout town by midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.73,0:45:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 假日杀手一出现 警方会准备好\NOne way or another, when holiday comes calling, we'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.86,0:45:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 这都是因为你\NYou know, this was all you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.61,0:45:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本想把他们关进高谭市监狱\NI wanted them in Gotham penitentiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.78,0:45:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哈维的主意 他是对的\NThis was Harvey. And he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.54,0:45:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日历人\NCalendar man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.13,0:46:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只在假日下手的杀手\NA killer who only works on holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.59,0:46:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是平安夜\NAnd it's December 24th.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.39,0:46:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想 你们何时才会来\NI was wondering when you'd get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.93,0:46:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没多少时间 戴伊\NWe don't have much time, day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.85,0:46:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在万圣节杀了强尼维提？\NWho killed Johnny viti on Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.10,0:46:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶手也在感恩节 杀了陈米奇和他的同夥\NThe same person who killed Mickey chen and his crew on Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.61,0:46:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得回答得再详细点\NWe need a better answer than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.69,0:46:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维提是罗马人的侄子\NViti was the Roman's nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.45,0:46:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马人是陈的雇主\NThe Roman was chen's employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.53,0:46:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 头号嫌犯就是罗马人\NFirst suspect is, therefore, the Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.46,0:46:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但鬼鬼祟祟不是法尔康尼的作风\NBut since sneaking around isn't really Falcone's style,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.80,0:46:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有第二位嫌疑犯\Nwe move on to the second suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个希望罗马帝国毁灭的人\NSomeone hoping for the fall of the Roman empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.22,0:46:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如 萨尔马洛尼\NLike sal maroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.39,0:46:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟其他人一样有嫌疑\NHe's as good a guess as any of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.89,0:46:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人是谁？\NWhat "others"?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.10,0:47:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们少一个人\NYou're down a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.15,0:47:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在浪费时间\NThis is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.23,0:47:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你带丹特先生来\NI told you to bring Mr. dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.78,0:47:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在外头不安全\NHe isn't safe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.70,0:47:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们进阿卡汉的检察官？\NThe da who put you all in arkham?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.95,0:47:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半数的病患看到他就会杀了他\NHalf the patients here would kill him on sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.95,0:47:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得他在外面才安全\Nso, I'd say out there is the only place he is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.00,0:47:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\NPerhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.96,0:47:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他不知道你在这里\NOr perhaps he doesn't know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.46,0:47:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许…\NPerhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.93,0:47:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检察官\NThe district attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.68,0:47:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嫌犯？\NIs a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.36,0:47:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 聪明 工於心计\NWell, of course. Intelligent, calculating,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.78,0:47:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算击溃卡麦法尔康尼\Nwith a mission to take down carmine Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.74,0:47:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都符合\NIt all fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.99,0:47:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维丹特不是凶手\NHarvey dent is not a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.41,0:48:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他过着双重生活\NUnless he's leading a double life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.92,0:48:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这位披风战士\NLike your caped crusader, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.96,0:48:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么找我来？\NWhy did you ask for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.63,0:48:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就能亲眼看到\NSo you could see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.47,0:48:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没空听你发疯\NI don't have time for your crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.85,0:48:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这个必要\NYou really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.26,0:48:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近来外头疯子可多了\NThere's lots of crazy out there these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.10,0:48:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为将他们清乾净了\NAnd just when you thought you'd cleaned it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.53,0:48:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是\NWhat a...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.69,0:48:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可笑\NJoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.29,0:48:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假期愉快\NHappy holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.71,0:48:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\NOpen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.60,0:49:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（丹特检察官 哈哈哈）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.60,0:49:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他派人去对付我的小孩\NHe had somebody get to my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.73,0:49:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果我不帮他\NIf... if I didn't help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.44,0:49:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.90,0:49:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维不安全\NHarvey isn't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.19,0:49:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.63,0:49:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人愉快的季节\N"Tis the season to be jolly
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.22,0:49:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面冷得要死\NOutside it's an awful chiller
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.39,0:49:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天 这个假期真迷人\NBoy, this holiday's a killer
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.06,0:49:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔达？是你吗？\NGilda? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.23,0:49:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“吉尔达”\N"Gilda"!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.74,0:49:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起来像吉尔达\NShe looked like a gilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.96,0:50:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.37,0:50:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 甜心\NRelax, lollipop!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是警方该管的\NPolice issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.09,0:50:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太呢？\NWhere's my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.76,0:50:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到她在做最後的采买\NShe's just where I left her, last-minute shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.43,0:50:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透露一下 她要送你袜子\NSpoiler alert. It's socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.81,0:50:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么？\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.56,0:50:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是我扮圣诞老人\NAww, I thought I was playing santi claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.52,0:50:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.73,0:50:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要消防车、橄榄球 还要\NI want a fire engine and a football and...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.07,0:50:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你一则讯息\NTo deliver a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.99,0:50:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下之後再谈\NPut the gun down and we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.79,0:50:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\NSure!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.26,0:51:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您怀疑得没错\NYour suspicions were correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.85,0:51:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说圣诞小丑今天已经恐吓了三个家庭\NA Santa clown has reportedly terrorized three families today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.81,0:51:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷 他们都姓丹特\NSir, they were all named "dent."
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.51,0:51:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会有那个？\NWhere did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.43,0:51:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？你的不见了吗？\NWhy? Ya missin' one?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.14,0:51:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要打打气\NYou could use some cheering up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.56,0:51:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有听过一个杀人小丑逃出精神病院\NHave ya heard the one about the murderous clown that escaped the asylum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.27,0:51:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑去把他关进精神病院的检察官家里？\Nand showed up at the home of the da who put him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.24,0:52:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直有传言 丹特检察官本人\NSee, there's a persistent rumor round these parts
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.53,0:52:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是外界看到的那样\Nthat da dent is more than he appears to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.37,0:52:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这座城市只容得下一个杀人狂\NBut there's only room for one homicidal maniac in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.25,0:52:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我听到快乐哈维丹特出门\NAnd if I hear that happy Harvey dent is steppin' out,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.05,0:52:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就让小吉尔达从此不用再采买\NI'll make sure little gilda doesn't have to clothes-shop
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.09,0:52:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公的衣服\Nfor hubby-wubby ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.72,0:52:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为很好笑吗？\NYou call that a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.81,0:52:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说到最精采的地方\NBut you haven't even heard the punchline!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.22,0:52:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个\NIt goes like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.15,0:52:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维\NHarvey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.78,0:52:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈维 听得见吗？\NHarvey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.12,0:52:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他跑去哪里吗？\NAny idea where he was heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.04,0:52:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马洛尼\NMaroni...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.71,0:52:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙日\NMangia.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.35,0:53:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友的脸怎么了 马洛尼？\NWhat happened to your friend's face, maroni?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.65,0:53:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 那你的脸呢？\NNothin'. What happened to yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.48,0:53:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混…\NOh, you mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.57,0:53:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我他说过的话\NTell me everything he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.49,0:53:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你松开我\NIf you get off of my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.12,0:53:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到的时候 他就在里面了\NHe was inside before we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.25,0:53:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了所有人 在豆汤里下毒\NTook out the whole staff, poisoned the fagioli.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.00,0:53:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时并不饿 但弗雷迪…\NI wasn't hungry, but, uh, Freddy, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.88,0:53:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我大概是走运吧\NI don't know. Guess I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.76,0:53:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他留你活口 为什么？\NNo. He let you live. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.80,0:53:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来像知道的样子吗？\NDo I look like I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.34,0:53:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿枪指着我的脸 说这里是他的地盘\NHe put a gun in my face and told me that this is his turf
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.39,0:53:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会除掉干涉他的人\Nand that he's cracking down on interlopers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.77,0:53:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我应该感谢他\NMaybe I should thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是怎么想的\NI don't know where you get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.77,0:54:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像小丑这种怪胎 以前只游走在法律边缘\NFreaks like this clown used to play way out on the fringe,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.44,0:54:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你出现後…\Nbut once you showed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.07,0:54:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 朋友\NRelax, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.29,0:54:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 以前这座城市很安宁\NYa know, things used to run smooth in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.33,0:54:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在有杀手鳄 杀手蛾和下水道殭屍\NNow, we got killer crocs and moths and sewer zombies,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.50,0:54:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更别提还有个杀人狂\Nnot to mention a homicidal maniac
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.96,0:54:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专挑节日出没 干掉黑帮成员\Nskulking around the holidays hittin' made men.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.18,0:54:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共同点是什么？\NWhat's the common thread? Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.31,0:54:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（小丑）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.64,0:54:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.39,0:54:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道？他是个疯子\NWho knows? He's a nutjob.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.27,0:54:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是他杀了法尔康尼的手下\NBut if he's the guy killin' Falcone's men,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.52,0:54:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他迟早会去对付卡麦\Nit's only a matter of time till he gets to old carmine himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.81,0:54:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该从那里查起\NMaybe start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.82,0:54:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不擅长当侦探 对吧？\NNot really much of a detective, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.14,0:55:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.82,0:55:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏青色、藏青色、深灰色、黑色\NNavy, Navy, charcoal, black.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.74,0:55:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 卡麦 试试不同颜色会怎样吗？\NReally, carm, is a splash of color too much to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.75,0:55:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少耍猴戏 要杀我就快动手\NStop clowning around. If you're gonna kill me, just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.75,0:55:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是杀手的脸吗？\NIs this the face of a killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.76,0:55:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是的\NI guess it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.43,0:56:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张 小家伙 我不会杀了你\NOh, relax, polpetto, I'm not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.14,0:56:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚不会\NNot tonight, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.11,0:56:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是圣诞节\NIt's Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.82,0:56:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.73,0:56:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚会有人死\NSomeone will die tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.99,0:56:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是你亲近的人\NProbably someone close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.82,0:56:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不想知道开枪的会是谁吗？\NDon't you want to know who's pulling the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.25,0:56:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我只是来说一声\NAnyhoo, I just popped in to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.00,0:56:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有假日杀手案的调查情报\Nif you hear any news about the holiday investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.34,0:56:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你通知我一声\NI'd like you to pass it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.21,0:56:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基於职业礼貌\NAs a professional courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.89,0:56:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的名片\NHere's my card!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.81,0:56:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐\NBuon natale!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.40,0:56:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐\NBuon natale.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.69,0:56:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真幽默\NI kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.41,0:56:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么？\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.71,0:57:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没打中\NMissed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.10,0:57:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我忘了什么吗？\NYou know what I forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.66,0:57:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好险\NWhoa! That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.38,0:58:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（圣诞节）
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.02,0:58:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爷 容我提醒您\NI would remind you, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.52,0:58:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法尔康尼先生为高谭儿童医院举办的年度义卖会\Nof Mr. Falcone's annual benefit for the Gotham children's clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.69,0:58:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建议您至少去露一次面\NIt would be advisable to show your face at least one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.74,0:59:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那间医院是令尊盖的\NYour father built that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.95,0:59:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他帮罗马人盖的\NHe helped the Roman build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.70,0:59:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算是做善事\NStill, a good cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.71,0:59:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说 参加游艇晚宴对您有益\NAnd, frankly, a night on a yacht could do you some good.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.21,0:59:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯尔小姐也会出席\NMiss Kyle will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.96,0:59:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个节日谋杀案\NThree murders on three holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者都跟法尔康尼有关\NEach of the victims a Falcone associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.01,0:59:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶器都是无法追踪的同一款枪\NAll shot with the same type of untraceable gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.56,0:59:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有目击者\NNo withesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.39,0:59:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯呢？\NSuspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.77,0:59:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔瓦多马洛尼\NSalvatore maroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.06,0:59:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的家族一直都不如罗马人\NHis family's always been second to the Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.94,0:59:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个野心勃勃的家伙\NHe's notoriously ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.07,0:59:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他在光天化日之下 杀了法尔康尼的手下\NBut he's killed Falcone's men in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.94,0:59:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要搞奇怪的假日杀人戏码？\NWhy the cloak-and-dagger holiday business?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.28,0:59:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉维提 法尔康尼的妹妹\NCarla viti, Falcone's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.53,0:59:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责他们的芝加哥据点\NRuns their Chicago operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.83,0:59:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有可能为了掌控家族 搞了这一出\NShe could be making a play for control of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在万圣节杀了独子？\NBy killing her only son on Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.17,0:59:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是罪犯\NShe is a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.21,0:59:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是杀人狂\NAnd he is a homicidal maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.30,0:59:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狱警作证 他在首起谋杀案前就逃了\NThe guard testified that he escaped before the first murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.38,1:00:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗马人自己杀的\NThe Roman himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.09,1:00:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼维提本来打算叛变\NJohnny viti was about to flip
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.18,1:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陈米奇有可能作证 是法尔康尼雇他去杀丹特\Nand Mickey chen could testify that Falcone ordered dent's murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.81,1:00:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有杀他们两人的动机\NHe had motive to silence them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.35,1:00:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么要杀自己的保镳？\NBut why kill his own bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.44,1:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以问您 为什么不怀疑第五位嫌疑犯吗？\NMay I ask why you're keeping the fifth suspect off the board?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.11,1:00:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不喜欢\NBecause I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.32,1:00:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但符合 不是吗？\NBut it fits. Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.70,1:00:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一心一意想击溃法尔康尼\NObsessed with taking down Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.16,1:00:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不把黑帮老大马洛尼和城里其他帮派放在眼里\NMore than boss maroni and every ambitious made man in town.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.95,1:00:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去年的枪枝使用申请没过\NHe was turned down for a gun license last year,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.79,1:00:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为心理评估报告指出 他有严重的精神错乱\Nwhen the psych eval showed some wild aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.96,1:00:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或根本另有其人？\NOr is it someone else entirely?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.63,1:00:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个我们从未考虑的人\NSomeone we haven't even considered.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.14,1:00:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来以为是要扫除街上的罪犯\NI thought this would be about sweeping criminals off the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.22,1:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们吓到改邪归正\Nmaybe scaring them straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.85,1:00:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到蝙蝠侠有一天还得当侦探\NI never thought that Batman was going to have to be a detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.39,1:00:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优秀的侦探\NA good one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.15,1:00:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我无法救他们呢 阿福？\NWhat if I can't save them, Alfred?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.11,1:01:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就见过这些痛苦 少爷\NI've seen these growing pains before, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.15,1:01:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有信心 到了最後\Nand I am confident that, in the end,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.57,1:01:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠侠会成为世人心目中的模样\Nthe Batman will be what the world needs him to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.87,1:01:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也能套用在布鲁斯韦恩身上\NThe same, I believe, should be said of Bruce Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.90,1:01:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位嘉宾\NMy distinguished guests,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.28,1:01:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位今晚莅临\Nit is my honor to welcome you here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.53,1:01:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见许多熟面孔 市长\NI see a lot of familiar faces. Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.29,1:01:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主教阁下\NYour eminence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.83,1:01:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我说的是萨尔马洛尼\NNo, I was talking to sal maroni.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.25,1:02:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔马洛尼在我的船上\NSal maroni. On my yacht.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.51,1:02:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如家父常说的 “靠近你的敌人\NIt's like my father always said, "keep your enemies close...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.89,1:02:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并随身携带手枪”\NAnd a loaded gun closer."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.90,1:02:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30年前 一群热心的高谭小子\NThirty years ago, a small group of concerned gothamites
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.15,1:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,携手打造一个\Njoined together to build something
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.82,1:02:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市政厅里唇枪舌战的政客盖不了的东西\Nthe politicians squabbling in the halls of government could not.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.36,1:02:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤玛士韦恩医生和我盖了儿童医院 保护众多家庭\NDr. Thomas Wayne and I built the children's clinic to protect families.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.53,1:02:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果各位了解我\NAnd if you know me,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.91,1:02:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就知道我最看重家人\Nyou know there is nothing more important to me than family.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.63,1:02:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐\NSo, buon anno!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.29,1:02:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢各位莅临及慷慨解囊\NThank you all for being here and for your generosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.96,1:02:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们打破去年的纪录\NLet's beat last year's total.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.30,1:02:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 只收现金\NRemember, cash only, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.31,1:03:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想感谢企业赞助商\NAlso, I would like to thank our corporate sponsors,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.90,1:03:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯德寰宇、索德可乐\Nkord omniversal, soder cola,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.07,1:03:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及成立十周年的高谭广播公司\Nand, for the 10th year running, Gotham broadcasting company.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.58,1:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NI'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.37,1:03:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扶你\NHere, let me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.42,1:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢谢你\NNo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.09,1:03:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说一件事 我保证就让各位享受派对\NOne more thing, and then I promise I'll let you enjoy the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.46,1:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想感谢一个人\NI would like to acknowledge someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.43,1:03:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所说的 我最看重家人\NAs I said, nothing is more important to me than family.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.55,1:03:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很後悔\NAnd, perhaps, my one regret
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.60,1:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这个人觉得 自己不是这个家的一分子\Nis making this man feel like he is not a part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.44,1:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在细节上 我们有时意见分歧\NWe have not always agreed on details.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.23,1:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都赞同几个重要的观念\NBut we agree on the most important things.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.49,1:03:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信家人\NWe believe in family.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.20,1:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信事业\NWe believe in business.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.41,1:03:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像今晚莅临的所有嘉宾一样\NAnd, like all of you here tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.96,1:04:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都相信高谭市\Nwe believe in Gotham city.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.59,1:04:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位先生女士 他就是我视如己出的\NLadies and gentlemen, the son I never had...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.88,1:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯韦恩先生\NMr. Bruce Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.13,1:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我好像看到他们了   -什么？\N- I think I see them!   - Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.55,1:04:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像很重要一样 我几乎都见不到你了\NAs if it matters. I hardly ever see you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.84,1:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说 没必要…\NI'm just saying, there's no need to...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.59,1:04:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 哈维\NHey, Harvey!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.35,1:05:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在值勤吗 队长？\NShouldn't you be working, captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.40,1:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在值勤啊\NI am.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.85,1:05:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是高谭市史上 最大规模的警察集结\NThis is the largest police presence this city's ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.98,1:05:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们圣诞节遭遇挫折\NWe got caught with our pants down on Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.98,1:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但假日杀手如果今晚想出手 只能自求多福了\Nbut heaven help holiday if he tries anything here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.99,1:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无时无刻都在值勤\NAlways on duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.99,1:05:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无时无刻\NAlways.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.70,1:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没带孩子出来？\NYou didn't bring the kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.50,1:05:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们今晚在我母亲家过夜\NThey're sleeping over at my mother's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.62,1:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次应该请你帮忙带孩子 吉尔达\NWe should try and hire you to sit next time, gilda.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.54,1:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很会带小孩\NI bet you're great with kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.59,1:05:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很多年没当保母了\NI haven't worked as a sitter in years.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.01,1:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她当保母赚钱念完法学院\NIt paid her way through law school.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.97,1:05:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是律师\NI didn't know you're a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.51,1:05:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是\NI was.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.51,1:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我什么都不是\NNow, I'm not anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.60,1:05:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞行员死了？确认\NDead pilot? Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.94,1:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地勤人员？确认\NGround crew? Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.65,1:05:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒气？确认\NPoison gas? Check.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.53,1:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候迎接新年了\NTime to ring in the new year.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.62,1:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位先生女士 请系好安全带\NLadies and gentlemen, please fasten your seatbelts,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.59,1:06:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道怎么驾驶这玩意儿\Nas I have no idea how to fly this thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.94,1:06:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像真正的派对\NLooks like a real party.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.82,1:06:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底在这里干嘛？\NSo, what the hell are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.57,1:06:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.20,1:06:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的直觉告诉我 今晚非来不可\NSomething tells me this is where I need to be tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.66,1:06:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…\NWe...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.75,1:06:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没好好谈过 我们应该谈谈\NLook, we haven't talked, and I think we should.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得无论问题在哪…\NI feel like whatever this is...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.21,1:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我们想为对方做什么 都失败了\NWhatever we've tried to be to one another is... unraveling.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.35,1:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都清楚为什么\NAnd we both know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.18,1:07:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从不谈这件事\NWe've never spoken of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.60,1:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实是 我俩差别很大\Nbut the truth is that you and I are two different people.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.77,1:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尝试的过程很有趣\NIt was fun to try...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.32,1:07:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可能永远无法结合\NBut I don't think we're ever gonna be able to put it all together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.99,1:07:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们就是无法变成\NI guess we're just not cut out for...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.62,1:07:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心目中的彼此\NWhatever this is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.95,1:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都过去了\NWas.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.88,1:07:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过别担心 回头见了\NDon't worry, though. I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.73,1:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候做的？\NWhen did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.90,1:07:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？\NDo what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.65,1:07:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我不注意时拿走我的表\NYou took my watch without me noticing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.65,1:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候做的？我很好奇\NSo, when did you do it? I'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.45,1:08:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我一句 布鲁斯\NTake it from me, Bruce,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.49,1:08:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 好奇心会害死你\Naround here, curiosity can get you killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.67,1:08:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没空\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.13,1:08:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.18,1:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.52,1:08:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想过个平凡的夜晚 我们能过个平凡的夜晚吗？\NI just want to have a normal night. Can we just have a normal night?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.10,1:08:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道什么叫平凡了\NI don't even know what that is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.19,1:08:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里好孤单\NI am alone here.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.94,1:08:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉自己没关系 一切都会好转 但没有\NI told myself it was okay because it would get better, but it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.95,1:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要一个人\NYou don't have to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.99,1:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈过生小孩的事\NWe've talked about having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.66,1:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法 你知道我没办法\NI can't! You know that I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.87,1:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许不用传统的方式\NMaybe not the old-fashioned way,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.42,1:08:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不代表我们不能试…\Nbut that doesn't mean that we can't try something...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.04,1:08:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想生孩子\NI don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.88,1:08:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想 因为我不能生 我不能生 因为我不想生\NI don't want it because I can't and I can't because I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.05,1:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以私下谈吗？\NCan we please talk about this in private?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.30,1:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 你为什么不能变得像…\NJesus, why can't you be more like...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.93,1:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像谁？\NMore like who?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.15,1:09:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一个普通人\NI'm only one man.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.90,1:09:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到\NI can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.15,1:09:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不想谈\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.28,1:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先失陪了\NExcuse us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.37,1:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆 你知道他们有这些问题吗？\NJim, did you know they're having these kinds of problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.21,1:09:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆？\NJim?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.21,1:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我看到了\NYeah. I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.09,1:09:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.88,1:09:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新年不快乐\NCrappy new year!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.44,1:09:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.08,1:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有罪行是否该被遗忘 而且不用审判…\NShould all offenses be forgot and never brought to trial...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.38,1:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我真蠢 安全阀 哈\NOh, silly me. The safety. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.97,1:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\NOoh, pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.07,1:10:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\NWell, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.54,1:10:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经济舱跟以前不一样了\NEconomy class ain't what she used to be. Ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.42,1:11:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤离这一区\NThis area needs to be clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.97,1:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-大家保持冷静   -这边\N- Everyone remain calm.   - This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.47,1:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-皮尔斯   -队长\N- Pearce!   - Captain, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.72,1:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我太太离开这里\NI need to get my wife out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.85,1:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 长官 请跟我来 夫人\NYes, sir! Follow me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.04,1:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想用这些噱头证明什么 小丑？\NWhat are you trying to prove with this stunt, joker?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.79,1:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证明？噱头？小丑？\NProve? Stunt? Joker?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.42,1:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 最後一个是对的\NNo, wait, that one's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.59,1:11:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你为什么要杀强尼维提？   -什么？\N- Why did you kill Johnny viti?   - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.51,1:11:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有陈米奇跟米洛斯葛莱帕？\NAnd Mickey chen and milos grappa?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.09,1:11:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是假日杀手？\NYou think I'm holiday?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.97,1:11:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我不知道你这么关心我\NOh, poppet, I didn't know you cared.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.77,1:12:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不是假日杀手\NOf course I'm not holiday!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.23,1:12:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果是他 怎么还会想杀他？\NIf I were him, why would I be trying to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.53,1:12:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀他？\NKill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.74,1:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是竞争对手啊\NHe's the competition!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.74,1:12:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像玉米罐头上说的\NAnd, like the corn kernel always says,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.45,1:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我只当最好的”\N"I won't be number two."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.75,1:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想杀了假日杀手…\NIf it's holiday you want dead...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.13,1:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛对整个高谭广场释放毒气？\NThen why gas everyone in Gotham square?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.63,1:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全市一半的人都在下面\NHalf the city's down there,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.76,1:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示假日杀手要嘛在里面 要嘛不在\Nwhich means holiday either is, or isn't!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.60,1:12:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一半的机率成功\NI have a 50-50 chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.06,1:12:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果失败了 至少我杀了很多无辜的人\NAnd if I fail, well, at least I've killed a lot of innocent people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.20,1:12:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 别杀我 先等我找到假日杀手\NNo, don't kill me! Not before I find out who holiday is!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.62,1:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你何必在乎？\NWhy do you care?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.91,1:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小笨蛋\NOh, you adorable fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.79,1:13:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不懂吗？我就跟你一样啊\NDon't you know by now? I'm just like youl!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.88,1:13:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都喜欢谜团\NWe both love a good puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.39,1:13:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等12点的钟声响起\NSo, when the clock strikes 12:00,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.39,1:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能得到一个吻吗？\Ndo I get a little kiss?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.41,1:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不要的意思吧\NWhoop! Taking that as a "no."
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.02,1:14:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望泡汤了\NThere goes my resolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.45,1:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开 快点 快让开\Nout of the way. Now! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.30,1:14:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是阿尔贝托吧？\NAlberto, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.26,1:14:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是赛琳娜\NSelina.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.31,1:14:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能问一个问题吗？\NCan I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.48,1:14:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试着想像 在这样的环境成长是什么感觉\NI'm trying to imagine what it's like to grow up around all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.90,1:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道\NI wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.86,1:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我学走路前 “家族先生”就把我送到海外寄宿学校\N"Mr. family" had me in boarding schools overseas before I could walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.57,1:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没关系 反正我也不能融入这里\NWhich is fine. I would have never fit in here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.91,1:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我毕业於牛津大学 我对商业的了解程度\NI'm an Oxford graduate who's learned more about business
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.42,1:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是家父永远也无法想像的 但是…\Nthan my father could ever hope to understand, yet...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.84,1:15:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你无法成为核心成员\NYou don't get a seat at the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.63,1:15:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我懦弱 我爱上了一个人\NBecause I'm "weak." I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.43,1:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么会懦弱呢？\NHow is that weak?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.76,1:15:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是正确的对象 对家族没有益处\NShe was the wrong woman. Wrong for the family.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.02,1:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他没有益处\NWrong for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.64,1:15:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时很渴望得到他的认可\NAnd, back then, I was so desperate for his approval.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.77,1:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她後来怎么了？\NWhat happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.57,1:15:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很惨\NTerrible things.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.15,1:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让他把她吓跑\NI let him scare her away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.99,1:15:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的是 这证明了他一开始就没看错我\NWhich, ironically, only proved that he was right about me in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.33,1:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱 丢人现眼\NWeak. An embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.17,1:15:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不是有意…\NI'm sorry, I don't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.63,1:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我觉得能跟你聊？\NWhy do I feel like I can talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.05,1:16:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…\NUh, I, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.05,1:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…\NI just...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.47,1:16:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 抱歉 我…\NOh, no. No, I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.56,1:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行…我们不能这样\NI can't... we can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.60,1:16:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离她远一点\NGet away from her.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.99,1:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯\NBruce!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.40,1:16:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 布鲁斯？韦恩？\NWait. Bruce? Wayne?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.24,1:16:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯韦恩是蝙蝠侠？\NBruce Wayne is the Batman?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.58,1:16:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝托法尔康尼是假日杀手\NAnd Alberto Falcone is holiday.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.37,1:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都有惊喜\NSurprises all around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.29,1:16:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？你被错的线索误导了 布鲁斯\NMe? You've been fed some bad clues, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.88,1:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是解开了谜题\NBut I still solved the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.59,1:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不被接受的儿子 本来能继承帝国 却被排除在外\NThe rejected son, born to inherit an empire, but cast aside.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.80,1:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了\NYou're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.43,1:16:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白你永远得不到王国的钥匙\NYou knew you'd never be handed the keys to the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.47,1:16:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是制造了危机 要破坏家族事业\Nso you manufactured a crisis that targets the family business.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.23,1:16:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.65,1:16:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能的继任者陆续遇害後\NWith potential successors dropping like flies,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.40,1:16:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲只将事业交由家族管理\Npoppa tightened the circle to family only,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.82,1:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是你首次进入了核心\Nand, for the first time, you were on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.86,1:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想管理这个家\NI don't want control of the family!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.57,1:17:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过\NI never did!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.70,1:17:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十 九 八 七 六 五\NTen! Nine! Eight! Seven! Six! Five!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.46,1:17:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四 三\NFour! Three!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.67,1:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意拿这个身分 交换普通的人生\NI would happily trade that for a normal life!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.58,1:17:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开高谭 到远方过日子\NTo spend my days as far away from Gotham as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.79,1:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二 一 新年快乐\NTwo! One! Happy new year!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.92,1:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结婚生子…\NTo get married, and have a child with...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.56,1:17:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\NOh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.45,1:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能懂的 你遗漏了太多线索\NYou couldn't know. You're missing so many pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.77,1:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（新年）
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.74,1:19:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.91,1:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆 我们到底在干什么？\NJim, what the hell are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.88,1:20:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜水员会花几天打捞 阿尔贝托法尔康尼剩下的遗体\NThe divers will be fishing out parts of Alberto Falcone for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.88,1:20:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五叶螺旋桨以最慢速运行 这样卷进去\NFive-bladed prop on its slowest speed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.72,1:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死法真惨烈\NHell of a way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.05,1:20:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是他的死因\NThat isn't how he went.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.35,1:20:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在落水前就被假日杀手枪杀了\NHe was shot by holiday before going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.14,1:20:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿尔贝托不是假日杀手？\NHang on. Alberto wasn't holiday?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.31,1:20:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以为他是\NI thought he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.73,1:20:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是奥坎剃刀原则 吉姆 最简单的解决方法\NIt was occam's razor, Jim, the simplest solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.73,1:20:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是错的\NBut it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.07,1:20:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去船上找阿尔贝托法尔康尼\NI went there for Alberto Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.49,1:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我要阻止他\NI thought I was supposed to stop him,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.91,1:20:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我应该是要救他才对\Nbut I was supposed to save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.58,1:20:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是清白的 但现在他死了\NHe was innocent. And now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.67,1:20:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须再谨慎点\NI needed to be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.38,1:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是\NWe all did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.76,1:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都是\NAll of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.55,1:20:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须派维安人员保护卡麦法尔康尼\NYou have to put a protective detail on carmine Falcone.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.39,1:20:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他肯让你这么做的话\NIf he'll even let you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.56,1:21:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们起初是要击垮罗马人\NDo you realize we started out trying to take down the Roman,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.73,1:21:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在却是要救他吗？\Nand, now, we're trying to save him?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.73,1:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成这样的？\NWhen did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.57,1:21:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有更好的问题\NI have a better question.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.90,1:21:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果阿尔贝托法尔康尼不是假日杀手 那谁才是？\NIf Alberto Falcone wasn't holiday... Then who is?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.91,1:21:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的下个目标是谁？\NAnd who's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.60,1:21:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（谨以本片纪念娜娅里维拉）
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.78,1:24:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿我们的兄弟长眠於此 直到蒙主召唤\NGrant that our brother may sleep here in peace until you awaken him to glory,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.79,1:24:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为您代表复活与生命\Nfor you are the resurrection and the life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.12,1:24:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,届时他将与您面对面\NThen he will see you face to face
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.75,1:24:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您让他看见光辉\Nand in your light will see light
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.34,1:24:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白上帝的璀璨之处\Nand know the splendor of god.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.80,1:24:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.05,1:24:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.36,1:24:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯\NBruce.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.15,1:24:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借一步说话\NA word.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.45,1:24:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡麦 需要我帮忙的地方尽管说\NCarmine. If there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.28,1:24:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我要你帮什么忙 你却一再拒绝我\NYou know what I want you to do but, time and time again, you refuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.29,1:24:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦恩基金会不是让黑帮洗钱的地方\NThe Wayne foundation isn't a money-laundering outfit for the mob.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.83,1:24:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不是 只要我还是主席\NAnd it won't be, so long as I'm in control.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.92,1:25:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\NOf course.
